    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight dark:text-white sm:text-3xl mb-2">Dr.Ketan Ginoya </h2> <br/>

<p>Dr. Ketan Ginoya is a highly skilled and compassionate general dentist with over a decade of experience in delivering exceptional dental care. Graduating with honors from the prestigious Boston University Goldman School of Dental Medicine in 2011, Dr. Ginoya has since dedicated his career to helping patients achieve optimal oral health and beautiful smiles.</p><br/>

<p>With a foundation in dental excellence, Dr. Ginoya also holds a Bachelor of Dental Surgery degree from  Rajiv Gandhi University of Health and Science, Bangalore, India. Demonstrating a commitment to lifelong learning, Dr. Ginoya has earned the Fellowship in the Academy of General Dentistry (FAGD), a testament to his extensive knowledge and expertise in the field.</p><br/>

<p>A strong advocate for continuous education and professional growth, Dr. Ginoya is an active member of several esteemed organizations, including the American Dental Association and the Academy of General Dentistry. His dedication to advancing his skills is reflected in his role as a Kois Center Mentor, where he guides other dental professionals in achieving clinical excellence.</p> <br/>

<p>Dr. Ginoya has completed extensive continuing education, including advanced training in implantology with Dr. Arun Garg, esthetic dentistry with Dr. Frank Spears at Spears Education, and comprehensive courses in composite techniques, hard and soft tissue augmentation, and zygomatic implants. His expertise in these areas allows him to offer cutting-edge dental solutions tailored to the unique needs of each patient.</p><br/>

<p>Whether it's enhancing a patient's smile with Invisalign, performing bone grafting, or conducting maxillary sinus augmentations, Dr. Ginoya combines his vast clinical experience with a patient-centered approach to ensure the best outcomes.</p> <br/>

<p>When you choose Dr. Ketan Ginoya, you are choosing a dentist who is not only deeply knowledgeable but also genuinely invested in your oral health and well-being. With a passion for dentistry and a commitment to excellence, Dr. Ginoya is dedicated to helping you achieve the smile you've always wanted.</p>
<br/>
  </Fragment>

